  m_text: "Dev Log Version 1.0.4\n\nBugs Fixed: \n\nFixed Backwards fire Skill not
    shooting backwards for some weapons\n\nFixed Extra life skill\n\nFixed XP Buff
    Game Setting not working\n\nAdded:\n\nExperience Points: Enemies will now drop
    experience points that need to be picked up to gain xp.\n\n\nAdded An option
    for particle trails on weapons and ships Instead of the line rendered trails.
    This Option also adds \"simulated\" Explosion when enabled.\n\nChanged the background
    from a repeating sprite to a simulated particle background."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b03b992b2252dab4c9668a1b0eba5b93, type: 2}
