  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Dev Log Version 1.0


    Weapons:



    Missile: Shoots a missile out
    from the front of your ship, and is the base weapon.



    Damage 20, Attack
    Speed 1, Projectile Speed 20





    Nuke: Shoots a nuke out dealing a lot of
    damage but having a high fire delay.



    Damage 60, Attack Speed 5, Projectile
    Speed 16



    Minigun: Shoots a burst of 20 bullets dealing small but a rapid
    amount of damage.



    Damage 8, Attack Speed 0.01, Projectile Speed 24



    Homing
    Missile: Shoots a slower Missile that homes to the closest enemy.



    Damage
    40, Attack Speed 1.5, Projectile Speed 25



    Flak: Shoots a spread of 3 bullets
    .



    Damage 20, Attack Speed 1.5, Projectile Speed 20



    Drones: Shoots
    a spread of 5 drones the homing to the closest enemy dealing small amounts of
    damage.



    Damage 5, Attack Speed 5, Projectile Speed 15





    Skills:



    Damage
    Boost: increases damage dealt for all weapons by 10%



    Speed Boost: increases
    player movement speed by 10%



    Double Shot: makes all weapon shoot 2 bullets
    per shot.



    Ammo Increase: increases maximum ammo by 10%



    Poison Damage:
    makes all weapons deal poison damage for 20% of the weapons damage.



    Life
    Steal: Gain 10% of your damage back as health for each hit.



    Health Increase:
    Increase your max health by 30%.



    Attack Speed Increase you guns attack
    speed by 10%.



    Extra Life: Gain an extra life to save you from death once.



    Exp
    Buff: Gain a buff of 5 exp per kill.



    Bullet Speed: Increase the projectile
    speed of your bullets by 10%.



    Burst Amount: Increase the Minigun''s burst
    amount by 5.



    Burst delay: reduce the delay between burst''s by 30%. (not
    sure if it''s works i have yet to properly test)



    Rapid Fire: removes the
    burst fire for the Minigun and switches it out for a full rapid fire.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b03b992b2252dab4c9668a1b0eba5b93, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -5243488613788892683, guid: b03b992b2252dab4c9668a1b0eba5b93, type: 2}
