  m_text: 'Dev Log Version 1.0.2a


    Bug Patch


    Fixed poison damage not dealing
    damage over time.



    Fixed solar systems not spawning.



    Increase the
    delay between when enemies with different weapons spawn.



    Added the leader
    board it is currently on for offline.



    Added Graphics settings for Bloom
    and Post processing.


'
